Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.83,0:00:56.88,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\bord0.5\3c&HA65CA0&}只要心中懷抱著信心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.88,0:01:02.88,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\bord0.5\3c&H71A400&}率直地認為澄澈的明天終將來到
